2
00:00:06,880 --> 00:00:11,080
I can't wait to crack open a cold one.

3
00:00:14,290 --> 00:00:18,880
 A turning point in life always comes without warning. 

4
00:00:18,880 --> 00:00:20,790
Sota?

5
00:00:21,890 --> 00:00:24,240
What are you doing here?

6
00:00:26,340 --> 00:00:28,370
Sota.

7
00:00:40,570 --> 00:00:44,220
 That night... 

8
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:56,210
 I became accused of murder. 

9
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:15,010
Tateishi-san. We've got trouble.

10
00:01:18,050 --> 00:01:23,610
When you returned home, your former partner, Aoki Sota-san, was found dead.

11
00:01:24,580 --> 00:01:26,060
Yes, Sir.

12
00:01:26,060 --> 00:01:29,410
Was there any trouble between you and Aoki-san?

13
00:01:31,340 --> 00:01:33,000
No, Ma'am.

14
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:36,210
And yet, he was found murdered in your home.

15
00:01:36,790 --> 00:01:40,260
Sir, I am innocent.

16
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:45,150
We shall investigate that matter with your utmost cooperation.

17
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:50,620
 Sota has died. 

18
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:56,180
 I was devastated to know he cheated on me, and now he's gone. 

19
00:01:57,210 --> 00:02:00,510
 I cursed Sota for what he had done. 

20
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:04,250
 But our time together wasn't all bad. 

21
00:02:05,140 --> 00:02:07,300
 He's gone. 

22
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:09,790
 He's really, truly gone. 

